{"tid":1698622,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請唔好再用懲罰黃店黎包裝你去飲飲食食","createTime":"2019-11-07T15:23:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T08:58:25.000Z","uid":335656,"like":7,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"be2a89762c09d39a1dd9a2e9254085a110e0b0de","tid":1698622,"uid":335656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:23:12.000Z","msg":"如題。<br />\n<br />\n首先，而家咁混亂既環境你有無足夠既<span style=\"color: red;\">資訊、智慧</span>去分辨佢係真黃定扮黃？<br />\n<br />\n第二，「黃店」背後既<span style=\"color: red;\">供應商 地產商</span>又一定係黃？你咁樣咪一樣比錢佢賺。你地咁樣係唔會令佢地驚架<br />\n<br />\n第三，而家係<span style=\"color: red;\">打緊仗</span> 成日話要<span style=\"color: red;\">攬炒</span> 唔係<span style=\"color: red;\">罷消費 走資金</span> 只保持最低限度消費咩？<br />\n<br />\n最後，問心嗰句 你心入面係真係諗住<span style=\"color: red;\">幫同路人</span> 定諗住<span style=\"color: red;\">打卡拎光環當自己付出左</span> 定係<span style=\"color: red;\">純粹想食好西</span>？<br />\n<br />\n請大家要時刻警醒自己 我地仲未贏 仲未可以係煲底下相見 真係<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好懶</span> 唔好因應潮流而扭曲左<span style=\"color: red;\">初心</span> 同路人固然要支持 但唔應該本末倒置 <span style=\"color: red;\">為消費而消費</span> 變相促進經濟"},{"pid":"e0df973bec846547c3bacd1a178c1f5f4b5a5485","tid":1698622,"uid":201604,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:24:27.000Z","msg":"懲罰黃店唔代表唔做其他野<br />\n而且咁樣可以搞死藍店"},{"pid":"9f22c253586ac6dc3451427251a7b546c1668311","tid":1698622,"uid":23451,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:26:58.000Z","msg":"唔撚駛食飯咩on9"},{"pid":"6b3a69e088de5f078055453ca513fa7dc537b869","tid":1698622,"uid":194894,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:27:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果連供應商地產商都要睇埋黃定藍，我驚連香都無得食咋"},{"pid":"75a48f9c1550900ad22e6ea2b055d10bae3a6ec8","tid":1698622,"uid":115655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:27:36.000Z","msg":"好多嘢可以一齊做"},{"pid":"df576ee935826703a